def insert_before_character(string):
    return string.replace('o', 'ao')

print(insert_before_character('Hello world!'))  # Halloa world!
print(insert_before_character('Python is awesome!'))  # Pythaoan is aweaosome!
print(insert_before_character('I love coding!'))  #I love coding!
